{"name": "text-games", "metadata": {"name": "text-games", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/Sriganth-byte/Python_Text_Games", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A collection of text-based games in Python.", "upload_time": 1735127477}, "documentation": ["# Text Games\r\n\r\n`text_games is a Python module that offers a collection of simple, text-based games for fun and learning.\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n\r\nThe module includes the following games:\r\n1. **Hangman**: Guess the hidden word letter by letter.\r\n2. **Number Guesser**: Guess a random number within a certain range.\r\n3. **Rock-Paper-Scissors**: Play against the computer.\r\n4. **Riddle Game**: Solve riddles within a limited number of attempts.\r\n5. **Word Scramble**: Unscramble the shuffled letters to form a word.\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\n\r\nYou can install the module via `pip`:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npip install text-games\r\n\r\nUSAGE\r\n\r\nfrom text_games import games\r\n\r\n# Play Hangman\r\ngames.hangman()\r\n\r\n# Play Number Guesser\r\ngames.number_guesser()\r\n\r\n# Play Rock-Paper-Scissors\r\ngames.rock_paper_scissors()\r\n\r\n# Play Riddle Game\r\ngames.riddle_game()\r\n\r\n# Play Word Scramble\r\ngames.word_scramble()\r\n\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "text_games", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "text_games.hangman", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.hangman", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.number_guesser", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.number_guesser", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.riddle_game", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.riddle_game", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.rock_paper_scissors", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.rock_paper_scissors", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.word_scramble", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.word_scramble", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "text_games.games", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "text_games.games.hangman", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Play a game of Hangman."]}, {"name": "text_games.games.number_guesser", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Play a Number Guesser game."]}, {"name": "text_games.games.rock_paper_scissors", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Play a Rock-Paper-Scissors game."]}, {"name": "text_games.games.riddle_game", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Play a Riddle Game."]}, {"name": "text_games.games.word_scramble", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Play a Word Scramble game."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "text_games.games.hangman", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.hangman", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.games.number_guesser", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.number_guesser", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.games.riddle_game", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.riddle_game", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.games.rock_paper_scissors", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.rock_paper_scissors", "project": null}}, {"name": "text_games.games.word_scramble", "xref": {"fqname": "text_games.games.word_scramble", "project": null}}]}]}